  +vlc-1.2.0_pre3.ebuild:
  bump to pre3

  27 Dec 2011; Mark Loeser <halcy0n@gentoo.org> vlc-1.1.13.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc/ppc64; bug #395543

  26 Dec 2011; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> -vlc-1.1.12-r1.ebuild,
  -vlc-1.1.12-r2.ebuild:
  remove old

  21 Dec 2011; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> vlc-1.1.13.ebuild:
  Stable for X86, wrt security bug #395543

  21 Dec 2011; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> vlc-1.1.13.ebuild:
  Stable for AMD64, wrt security bug #395543

