*vlc-1.1.12-r1 (09 Dec 2011)

  09 Dec 2011; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> +vlc-1.1.12-r1.ebuild,
  vlc-1.1.9999.ebuild, vlc-1.2.9999.ebuild, vlc-9999.ebuild:
  Force using and initialising libX11 for threads in the xosd module. This
  should fix bug #393439

  09 Dec 2011; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> vlc-1.2.9999.ebuild,
  vlc-9999.ebuild:
  pass --without-tuning to configure so that we dont get a -mtune appended to
  our cflags

*vlc-1.2.9999 (07 Dec 2011)

  07 Dec 2011; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> +vlc-1.2.9999.ebuild:
  add live ebuild for 1.2 branch

