  fix libbluray dep

  06 Dec 2011; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> vlc-1.1.12.ebuild,
  vlc-1.1.9999.ebuild, vlc-1.2.0_pre1.ebuild, vlc-9999.ebuild:
  improve font deps, by Luke-Jr, bug #392689: use any ttf font when fontconfig
  is enabled and force dejavu if not because its accessed by path

  11 Nov 2011; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> vlc-1.1.12.ebuild,
  vlc-1.1.9999.ebuild:
  libnotify plugin requires gtk+:2 even on 1.1, bug #386743 by
  paul.wap@gmail.com

  06 Nov 2011; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> -vlc-1.1.11.ebuild:
  remove old

  05 Nov 2011; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> vlc-1.1.12.ebuild:
